data.description: Welcome home! This charming 2-story residence boasts four spacious bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, and a perfect blend of modern elegance and comfortable living. As you approach the home, you'll be greeted by its inviting curb appeal, featuring a well-maintained front yard. Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by an open and light-filled floor plan designed to accommodate both family living and entertaining with ease. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space, and a convenient breakfast bar. Upstairs, you'll find four generously-sized bedrooms, each offering ample closet space and large windows that flood the rooms with natural light. The backyard an ideal spot for outdoor gatherings and barbecues. Located in a quiet well-established neighborhood.
